                     <interp inst="t18300218-38-person340" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . One glass is mine; this other glass belongs to a publican who lives about one hundred yards from me - he is on the Jury at Guildhall, and cannot attend.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was in great distress, and had been out of work a long time.</p>
               <p>
